    <entry>
      <title>使用 npm 安装和配置 Hexo Butterfly 主题完整教程</title>
      <link href="/2025/08/24/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20npm%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%20Hexo%20Butterfly%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/08/24/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20npm%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%20Hexo%20Butterfly%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文将为您提供从零开始使用 npm 安装和配置 Hexo Butterfly 主题的完整指南，包括主题安装、基本配置和部署流程。</p><h2 id="第一阶段：安装-Butterfly-主题"><a href="#第一阶段：安装-Butterfly-主题" class="headerlink" title="第一阶段：安装 Butterfly 主题"></a>第一阶段：安装 Butterfly 主题</h2><h3 id="步骤-1-安装-Butterfly-主题包"><a href="#步骤-1-安装-Butterfly-主题包" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1: 安装 Butterfly 主题包"></a>步骤 1: 安装 Butterfly 主题包</h3><p>在您的 Hexo 博客根目录（包含 <code>_config.yml</code>、<code>package.json</code> 等文件的目录）中打开终端，执行以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 Butterfly 主题</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-theme-butterfly</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装主题所需的渲染器（非常重要！）</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 字数统计和阅读时间估算</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-wordcount --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 本地搜索支持</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 相关文章推荐</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-related-popular-posts --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="步骤-2-启用主题"><a href="#步骤-2-启用主题" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2: 启用主题"></a>步骤 2: 启用主题</h3><p>打开 Hexo 主配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code>（在博客根目录），找到 <code>theme</code> 设置项，将其修改为：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">butterfly</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存文件。</p><h2 id="第二阶段：配置-Butterfly-主题"><a href="#第二阶段：配置-Butterfly-主题" class="headerlink" title="第二阶段：配置 Butterfly 主题"></a>第二阶段：配置 Butterfly 主题</h2><h3 id="步骤-1-创建主题配置文件"><a href="#步骤-1-创建主题配置文件" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1: 创建主题配置文件"></a>步骤 1: 创建主题配置文件</h3><p>在博客根目录执行以下命令，将主题的默认配置node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-butterfly&#x2F;_config.yml复制到您的博客根目录并重命名为_config.butterfly.yml</p><p><strong>重要</strong>：此步骤创建了主题的配置文件副本，您应该只修改这个副本文件，而不是直接修改 <code>node_modules</code> 中的原始文件。</p><h3 id="步骤-2-基本配置指南"><a href="#步骤-2-基本配置指南" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2: 基本配置指南"></a>步骤 2: 基本配置指南</h3><p>打开 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 文件，以下是一些基本配置项：</p><h4 id="网站基本信息"><a href="#网站基本信息" class="headerlink" title="网站基本信息"></a>网站基本信息</h4><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 网站图标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">favicon:</span> <span class="string">/img/favicon.png</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 网站标题和副标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">site:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">您的博客名称</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">您的博客副标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 个人信息</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">img:</span> <span class="string">/img/avatar.png</span>  <span class="comment"># 头像图片路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">effect:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>          <span class="comment"># 头像旋转效果</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="菜单导航"><a href="#菜单导航" class="headerlink" title="菜单导航"></a>菜单导航</h4><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">首页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">归档:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-folder-open</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">关于:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 添加更多菜单项...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="主题外观"><a href="#主题外观" class="headerlink" title="主题外观"></a>主题外观</h4><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 主题配色方案</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme_color:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">main:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#49B1F5&quot;</span>      <span class="comment"># 主题主颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">paginator:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#00C4B6&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 分页器颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">button:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#FF7242&quot;</span>    <span class="comment"># 按钮颜色</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 暗黑模式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">darkmode:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">button:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>         <span class="comment"># 显示暗黑模式切换按钮</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="社交链接"><a href="#社交链接" class="headerlink" title="社交链接"></a>社交链接</h4><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">github:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/yourname</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fab</span> <span class="string">fa-github</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">twitter:</span> <span class="string">https://twitter.com/yourname</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fab</span> <span class="string">fa-twitter</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">email:</span> <span class="string">mailto:your-email@example.com</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-envelope</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 更多社交平台...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文章页面设置"><a href="#文章页面设置" class="headerlink" title="文章页面设置"></a>文章页面设置</h4><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">copyright:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>       <span class="comment"># 启用文章版权声明</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">license:</span> <span class="string">CC</span> <span class="string">BY-NC-SA</span> <span class="number">4.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">license_url:</span> <span class="string">https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">reward:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>       <span class="comment"># 启用打赏功能</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">wechatpay:</span> <span class="string">/img/reward/wechatpay.png</span>  <span class="comment"># 微信支付二维码</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">alipay:</span> <span class="string">/img/reward/alipay.png</span>        <span class="comment"># 支付宝二维码</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="评论系统（以-Waline-为例）"><a href="#评论系统（以-Waline-为例）" class="headerlink" title="评论系统（以 Waline 为例）"></a>评论系统（以 Waline 为例）</h4><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">waline:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">serverURL:</span> <span class="string">https://your-domain.com</span> <span class="comment"># Waline 服务端地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">mp</span>         <span class="comment"># 评论者头像样式</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">requiredFields:</span> [] <span class="comment"># 必填字段，可选[&#x27;nick&#x27;,&#x27;mail&#x27;]</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">lang:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span>        <span class="comment"># 语言</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="步骤-3-本地测试配置"><a href="#步骤-3-本地测试配置" class="headerlink" title="步骤 3: 本地测试配置"></a>步骤 3: 本地测试配置</h3><p>完成基本配置后，在本地测试您的博客：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理并启动本地服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问 <code>http://localhost:4000</code> 查看主题效果。如果发现样式问题，请确保已正确安装所需的渲染器。</p><h2 id="第三阶段：部署到线上"><a href="#第三阶段：部署到线上" class="headerlink" title="第三阶段：部署到线上"></a>第三阶段：部署到线上</h2><h3 id="步骤-1-提交更改到-Git"><a href="#步骤-1-提交更改到-Git" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1: 提交更改到 Git"></a>步骤 1: 提交更改到 Git</h3><p>将您的配置更改提交到 Git 仓库：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加所有更改</span></span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 提交更改</span></span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;feat: 安装并配置Butterfly主题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 推送到远程仓库</span></span><br><span class="line">git push origin main</span><br><span class="line">git push gitee main  <span class="comment"># 如果使用Gitee备份</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="步骤-2-验证部署"><a href="#步骤-2-验证部署" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2: 验证部署"></a>步骤 2: 验证部署</h3><ol><li>Vercel 会自动检测 GitHub 仓库的更改并重新部署</li><li>访问您的 Vercel 域名（如 <code>xxx.vercel.app</code>）查看最新效果</li><li>如果使用 GitHub Pages，确保已开启 Pages 功能：<ul><li>进入 GitHub 仓库 → Settings → Pages</li><li>选择源为 “GitHub Actions” 或对应的分支</li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="第四阶段：高级配置与自定义"><a href="#第四阶段：高级配置与自定义" class="headerlink" title="第四阶段：高级配置与自定义"></a>第四阶段：高级配置与自定义</h2><h3 id="自定义样式"><a href="#自定义样式" class="headerlink" title="自定义样式"></a>自定义样式</h3><p>创建 <code>source/_data/styles.styl</code> 文件添加自定义 CSS：</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义样式示例</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.post-page</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.post-content</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">16px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="number">1.8</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义按钮样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.custom-btn</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="number">45deg</span>, <span class="number">#49B1F5</span>, <span class="number">#FF7242</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="number">8px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">padding</span>: <span class="number">10px</span> <span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: white <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 中启用自定义样式：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">inject:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">head:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&lt;link</span> <span class="string">rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="string">href=&quot;/css/custom.css&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">bottom:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&lt;script</span> <span class="string">src=&quot;/js/custom.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="添加自定义页面"><a href="#添加自定义页面" class="headerlink" title="添加自定义页面"></a>添加自定义页面</h3><p>创建关于页面：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑 <code>source/about/index.md</code>：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 关于我</span><br><span class="line">date: 2023-01-01 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">type: about</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这里写关于您的介绍...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="常见问题解决"><a href="#常见问题解决" class="headerlink" title="常见问题解决"></a>常见问题解决</h2><ol><li><p><strong>页面样式错乱</strong>：</p><ul><li>确保已安装所需渲染器：<code>npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</code></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>配置修改未生效</strong>：</p><ul><li>执行 <code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate</code> 重新生成</li><li>确保修改的是 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 而不是 <code>node_modules</code> 中的文件</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>本地正常但线上异常</strong>：</p><ul><li>检查 Vercel&#x2F;GitHub Pages 的构建日志</li><li>确保所有依赖已正确添加到 <code>package.json</code></li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="更多资源"><a href="#更多资源" class="headerlink" title="更多资源"></a>更多资源</h2><ol><li><a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">Butterfly 官方文档</a></li><li><a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">Hexo 官方文档</a></li><li><a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/">Butterfly 主题配置示例</a></li></ol><p>通过本教程，您应该已经成功安装并配置了 Butterfly 主题。如需进一步个性化，请参考 Butterfly 官方文档中的详细配置选项。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
