      <title>完整个人博客搭建指南：Hexo + GitHub + Vercel + Gitee</title>
      <link href="/2025/08/24/%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%EF%BC%9AHexo%20+%20GitHub%20+%20Vercel%20+%20Gitee/"/>
      <url>/2025/08/24/%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%EF%BC%9AHexo%20+%20GitHub%20+%20Vercel%20+%20Gitee/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>下面是一个从零开始的完整教程，教你如何使用 Hexo 创建博客，并部署到 GitHub Pages 和 Vercel，同时将代码备份到 Gitee。</p><h2 id="第一阶段：Hexo-GitHub-Pages-搭建"><a href="#第一阶段：Hexo-GitHub-Pages-搭建" class="headerlink" title="第一阶段：Hexo + GitHub Pages 搭建"></a>第一阶段：Hexo + GitHub Pages 搭建</h2><h3 id="步骤-1-环境准备"><a href="#步骤-1-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1: 环境准备"></a>步骤 1: 环境准备</h3><ol><li><p><strong>安装 Node.js</strong></p><ul><li>访问 <a href="https://nodejs.org/">Node.js 官网</a></li><li>下载并安装 LTS（长期支持版）</li><li>安装完成后，打开终端&#x2F;命令提示符，验证安装：<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>安装 Git</strong></p><ul><li>访问 <a href="https://git-scm.com/">Git 官网</a></li><li>下载并安装 Git</li><li>安装后配置全局用户信息：<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;你的用户名&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-2-安装并初始化-Hexo"><a href="#步骤-2-安装并初始化-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2: 安装并初始化 Hexo"></a>步骤 2: 安装并初始化 Hexo</h3><ol><li><p><strong>安装 Hexo CLI</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>初始化博客项目</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init my-blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> my-blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>本地预览</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在浏览器中访问 <code>http://localhost:4000</code> 查看博客</p></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-3-创建-GitHub-仓库"><a href="#步骤-3-创建-GitHub-仓库" class="headerlink" title="步骤 3: 创建 GitHub 仓库"></a>步骤 3: 创建 GitHub 仓库</h3><ol><li><p><strong>登录 GitHub</strong></p><ul><li>访问 <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a> 并登录</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>创建新仓库</strong></p><ul><li>点击右上角 “+” → “New repository”</li><li>仓库名格式: <code>你的用户名.github.io</code> (例如: <code>johnsmith.github.io</code>)</li><li>选择 “Public”</li><li>勾选 “Initialize this repository with a README”</li><li>点击 “Create repository”</li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-4-配置-Hexo-部署到-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#步骤-4-配置-Hexo-部署到-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="步骤 4: 配置 Hexo 部署到 GitHub Pages"></a>步骤 4: 配置 Hexo 部署到 GitHub Pages</h3><ol><li><p><strong>安装部署插件</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>修改博客配置</strong></p><ul><li>打开 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件</li><li>找到 <code>deploy</code> 部分，修改为：<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/你的用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>生成并部署</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>访问你的 GitHub Pages</strong></p><ul><li>打开浏览器访问 <code>https://你的用户名.github.io</code></li><li>你的博客已经上线了！</li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-5-日常写作流程"><a href="#步骤-5-日常写作流程" class="headerlink" title="步骤 5: 日常写作流程"></a>步骤 5: 日常写作流程</h3><ol><li><p><strong>创建新文章</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>编辑文章</strong></p><ul><li>使用任何文本编辑器编辑 <code>source/_posts/文章标题.md</code></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>本地预览</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>部署更新</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="第二阶段：添加-Vercel-部署"><a href="#第二阶段：添加-Vercel-部署" class="headerlink" title="第二阶段：添加 Vercel 部署"></a>第二阶段：添加 Vercel 部署</h2><h3 id="步骤-1-注册-Vercel"><a href="#步骤-1-注册-Vercel" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1: 注册 Vercel"></a>步骤 1: 注册 Vercel</h3><ol><li><strong>访问 <a href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel 官网</a></strong></li><li><strong>使用 GitHub 账号注册&#x2F;登录</strong></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-2-部署到-Vercel"><a href="#步骤-2-部署到-Vercel" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2: 部署到 Vercel"></a>步骤 2: 部署到 Vercel</h3><ol><li><p><strong>在 Vercel 中导入项目</strong></p><ul><li>点击 “Add New…” → “Project”</li><li>从 GitHub 仓库列表中选择你的博客仓库</li><li>点击 “Import”</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>配置项目设置</strong></p><ul><li>Framework Preset: 选择 “Hexo”</li><li>Build Command: 输入 <code>npm run build</code> 或 <code>hexo generate</code></li><li>Output Directory: 输入 <code>public</code></li><li>其他设置保持默认</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>部署</strong></p><ul><li>点击 “Deploy”</li><li>等待部署完成</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>访问你的 Vercel 博客</strong></p><ul><li>部署完成后，Vercel 会提供一个类似 <code>xxx.vercel.app</code> 的域名</li><li>点击即可访问你的博客</li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-3-配置自定义域名（可选）"><a href="#步骤-3-配置自定义域名（可选）" class="headerlink" title="步骤 3: 配置自定义域名（可选）"></a>步骤 3: 配置自定义域名（可选）</h3><ol><li><strong>在 Vercel 项目仪表板中</strong><ul><li>点击 “Settings” → “Domains”</li><li>输入你的自定义域名</li><li>按照提示配置 DNS 记录</li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="第三阶段：添加-Gitee-备份"><a href="#第三阶段：添加-Gitee-备份" class="headerlink" title="第三阶段：添加 Gitee 备份"></a>第三阶段：添加 Gitee 备份</h2><h3 id="步骤-1-创建-Gitee-账户和仓库"><a href="#步骤-1-创建-Gitee-账户和仓库" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1: 创建 Gitee 账户和仓库"></a>步骤 1: 创建 Gitee 账户和仓库</h3><ol><li><strong>访问 <a href="https://gitee.com/">Gitee</a> 并注册&#x2F;登录</strong></li><li><strong>创建新仓库</strong><ul><li>点击 “+” → “新建仓库”</li><li>仓库名: 与 GitHub 仓库同名 (例如: <code>你的用户名.gitee.io</code>)</li><li>选择 “公开”</li><li>点击 “创建”</li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-2-配置本地仓库连接两个远程源"><a href="#步骤-2-配置本地仓库连接两个远程源" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2: 配置本地仓库连接两个远程源"></a>步骤 2: 配置本地仓库连接两个远程源</h3><ol><li><p><strong>查看当前远程仓库</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote -v</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 应该显示连接到 GitHub 的 origin</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>添加 Gitee 作为第二个远程仓库</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote add gitee https://gitee.com/你的用户名/你的仓库名.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>验证两个远程仓库</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote -v</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 现在应该显示两个远程仓库: origin (GitHub) 和 gitee (Gitee)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="步骤-3-推送代码到两个仓库"><a href="#步骤-3-推送代码到两个仓库" class="headerlink" title="步骤 3: 推送代码到两个仓库"></a>步骤 3: 推送代码到两个仓库</h3><ol><li><strong>首次推送</strong><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 推送到 GitHub</span></span><br><span class="line">git push github main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 推送到 Gitee</span></span><br><span class="line">git push gitee main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>如果push到github时有下方报错<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push -u github master</span><br><span class="line">remote: Invalid username or token. Password authentication is not supported <span class="keyword">for</span> Git operations.</span><br><span class="line">fatal: Authentication failed <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/xxx/xxx.git/&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>解决方案： 使用clash verge代理</li><li>使用 HTTP 代理,端口需要去clash verge中看具体使用的是哪个端口<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7890</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 用完之后取消</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global --<span class="built_in">unset</span> http.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>生成新的 Classic Token（ghp_ 开头，repo 权限）<br>生成 Personal Access Token<br>登录 GitHub 网站：<a href="https://github.com/">https://github.com</a><br>点击右上角头像 → Settings<br>左侧菜单 → Developer settings<br>再左侧 → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic) 或 Fine-grained tokens<br>推荐先用 Classic Token（兼容性更好）<br>点击 Generate new token → Generate new token (classic)<br>填写信息：<br>Note: 比如 git-push-token<br>Expiration: 选择过期时间（建议 30 天或 90 天）<br>Scopes: 勾选 repo（这是最关键的权限）<br>点击 Generate token<br>⚠️ 复制生成的 token（一串字符，如 ghp_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX）<br>🔐 仅显示一次，关闭后就看不到了</li><li>推送<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push -u github master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>然后选token粘贴生成的token</li><li><strong>日常推送流程</strong><ul><li>每次更新后，同时推送到两个仓库：<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;更新描述&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git push github master</span><br><span class="line">git push gitee master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="第四阶段：自动化工作流"><a href="#第四阶段：自动化工作流" class="headerlink" title="第四阶段：自动化工作流"></a>第四阶段：自动化工作流</h2><h3 id="方案-A-手动同步（简单可靠）"><a href="#方案-A-手动同步（简单可靠）" class="headerlink" title="方案 A: 手动同步（简单可靠）"></a>方案 A: 手动同步（简单可靠）</h3><p>每次更新后执行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy  <span class="comment"># 部署到 GitHub Pages</span></span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;更新描述&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git push github master  <span class="comment"># 推送到 GitHub</span></span><br><span class="line">git push gitee master   <span class="comment"># 推送到 Gitee</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Vercel 会自动检测 GitHub 更新并部署</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="方案-B-使用-GitHub-Actions-自动同步到-Gitee"><a href="#方案-B-使用-GitHub-Actions-自动同步到-Gitee" class="headerlink" title="方案 B: 使用 GitHub Actions 自动同步到 Gitee"></a>方案 B: 使用 GitHub Actions 自动同步到 Gitee</h3><ol><li><p><strong>创建 GitHub Token</strong></p><ul><li>在 GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens</li><li>生成新 token，勾选 <code>repo</code> 权限</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>在 Gitee 创建私人令牌</strong></p><ul><li>在 Gitee → 设置 → 私人令牌</li><li>生成新令牌，勾选 <code>projects</code> 权限</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>在 GitHub 仓库中添加 Secrets</strong></p><ul><li>进入你的 GitHub 仓库 → Settings → Secrets → Actions</li><li>添加以下 Secrets:<ul><li><code>GITEE_TOKEN</code>: 你的 Gitee 私人令牌</li><li><code>GITEE_USERNAME</code>: 你的 Gitee 用户名</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>创建 GitHub Actions 工作流</strong></p><ul><li>在项目根目录创建 <code>.github/workflows/sync-to-gitee.yml</code></li><li>添加以下内容：</li></ul></li></ol><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Sync</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">Gitee</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">on:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">push:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">branches:</span> [<span class="string">master</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">jobs:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">sync:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="string">ubuntu-latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">steps:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Sync</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">Gitee</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">wearerequired/git-mirror-action@master</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">env:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">SSH_PRIVATE_KEY:</span> <span class="string">$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">secrets.GITEE_TOKEN</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">with:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">source-repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">github.repository</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;.git</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">destination-repo:</span> <span class="string">git@gitee.com:$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">secrets.GITEE_USERNAME</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;/$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">github.event.repository.name</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;.git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>你现在已经拥有了一个完整的博客系统：</p><ol><li><strong>写作</strong>：使用 Hexo 在本地用 Markdown 写作</li><li><strong>部署</strong>：<ul><li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong>: 主要托管平台</li><li><strong>Vercel</strong>: 全球 CDN 加速，自动化部署</li></ul></li><li><strong>备份</strong>：代码同步到 Gitee，确保数据安全</li><li><strong>自动化</strong>：通过 GitHub Actions 实现自动同步</li></ol><h3 id="访问方式："><a href="#访问方式：" class="headerlink" title="访问方式："></a>访问方式：</h3><ul><li>GitHub Pages: <code>https://你的用户名.github.io</code></li><li>Vercel: <code>https://你的项目名.vercel.app</code> (或你的自定义域名)</li><li>Gitee: 仅作为代码备份，不直接用于访问</li></ul><p>这个方案结合了多个平台的优点，提供了高速访问、自动化部署和数据备份的完整解决方案。如果在实施过程中遇到任何问题，可以随时提问！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
